As I look at the  12th May, there is luggage, then kids t-shirts, more luggage, shoes, beach toys, more shoes, a kids clock, books, another kids clock, more t-shirts, a watch, a ball, yet another kids clock, another t-shirt‚Ä¶...oh, and what I was really looking for: digital luggage scales.   ‚Ä¢  Finally, where is the shopping list?? Before I could short list items and even link it to my Google calendar, now the only option I have is to order the items online. There are five ALDIs within a couple of miles of my home, so I have no interest in mail order.
